decks.notes: The deck focuses on utilizing countermagic, draw spells, and extra turn effects to control the game and disrupt the opponent's strategy. By efficiently countering threats, finding key cards with spells like Intuition and Merchant Scroll, and taking extra turns with cards like Time Warp and Turnabout, the deck aims to outmaneuver the opponent and secure a victory. Lier, Disciple of the Drowned's ability to cast spells from the graveyard further enhances the deck's ability to maintain control and outpace the opponent. With a focus on card advantage, tempo, and disruption, this deck aims to carve out a path to victory through strategic play and resource management.
